Name: Season
Description: The college basketball season of the game

Name: StartYear
Description: The year in which the season started

Name: EndYear
Description: The year in which the season ended

Name: Description
Description: The description of this season for display purposes (e.g. 2017-18; 2018-19; etc)

Name: RegularSeasonStartDate
Description: The start date of the regular season

Name: PostSeasonStartDate
Description: The start date of the postseason

Name: ApiSeason
Description: The string to pass into subsequent API calls in the season parameter

Name: ConferenceID
Description: The ID of the team's conference

Name: Name
Description: The name of the team's conference

Name: Teams
Description: The college teams within this conference

Name: TeamID
Description: The auto-generated unique ID of the Team

Name: [Key]
Description: Abbreviation of the team (e.g. OU; TTU; USC; UK; etc.)

Name: Active
Description: Whether or not this team is active

Name: School
Description: The school of the team (e.g. Oklahoma University; Texas Tech University; University of Southern California; Kentucky University; etc)

Name: Name
Description: The mascot of the team (e.g. Sooners; Red Raiders; Trojans; Wildcats; etc.)

Name: ApRank
Description: The AP Rank of the team

Name: Wins
Description: The total number of wins by the school

Name: Losses
Description: The total number of losses by the school

Name: ConferenceWins
Description: The total number of conference wins by the school

Name: ConferenceLosses
Description: The total number of conference losses by the school

Name: GlobalTeamID
Description: A globally unique ID for this team. This value is guaranteed to be unique across all sports/leagues.

Name: ConferenceID
Description: The ID of the team's conference

Name: Conference
Description: The name of the team's conference

Name: TeamLogoUrl
Description: The url of the team logo image.

Name: ShortDisplayName
Description: The short display name of the team

Name: Stadium
Description: The home stadium of the team

Name: GameID
Description: The unique ID of this game

Name: Season
Description: The College Basketball season of the game

Name: SeasonType
Description: The type of season that this record corresponds to (1=Regular Season; 2=Preseason; 3=Postseason; 4=Offseason; 5=AllStar).

Name: Status
Description: Indicates the game's status. Possible values include: Scheduled; InProgress; Final; F/OT; Suspended; Postponed; Canceled

Name: Day
Description: The date of the game

Name: DateTime
Description: The date and time of the game

Name: AwayTeam
Description: The abbreviation of the Away Team

Name: HomeTeam
Description: The abbreviation of the Home Team

Name: AwayTeamID
Description: The unique ID of the away team

Name: HomeTeamID
Description: The unique ID of the home team

Name: AwayTeamScore
Description: Total number of points the away team scored in this game

Name: HomeTeamScore
Description: Total number of points the home team scored in this game

Name: Updated
Description: The timestamp of when this game was last updated (in US Eastern Time)

Name: Period
Description: The current half of the game (Possible Values: 1; 2; Half; OT; F; F/OT; NULL)

Name: TimeRemainingMinutes
Description: Number of minutes remaining in the half

Name: TimeRemainingSeconds
Description: Number of seconds remaining in the half

Name: PointSpread
Description: The oddsmaker Point Spread at game start from the perspective of the HomeTeam (negative numbers indicate the HomeTeam is favored; positive numbers indicate the AwayTeam is favored). This is updated once daily at 4:00 AM ET.

Name: OverUnder
Description: The oddsmaker Over/Under at game start. This is updated once daily at 4:00 AM ET.

Name: AwayTeamMoneyLine
Description: Money line from the perspective of the away team. This is updated once daily at 4:00 AM ET.

Name: HomeTeamMoneyLine
Description: Money line from the perspective of the home team. This is updated once daily at 4:00 AM ET.

Name: GlobalGameID
Description: A globally unique ID for this game. This value is guaranteed to be unique across all sports/leagues.

Name: GlobalAwayTeamID
Description: A globally unique ID for the away team. This value is guaranteed to be unique across all sports/leagues.

Name: GlobalHomeTeamID
Description: A globally unique ID for the home team. This value is guaranteed to be unique across all sports/leagues.

Name: TournamentID
Description: The unique ID of the tournament

Name: Bracket
Description: The bracket of the tournament

Name: Round
Description: The current round of the tournament

Name: AwayTeamSeed
Description: The seed of the away team

Name: HomeTeamSeed
Description: The seed of the home team

Name: AwayTeamPreviousGameID
Description: The unique ID of the away team's previous game (This gameid will be inaccurate/invalid in free trial as it is scrambled)

Name: HomeTeamPreviousGameID
Description: The unique ID of the home team's previous game (This gameid will be inaccurate/invalid in free trial as it is scrambled)

Name: AwayTeamPreviousGlobalGameID
Description: The unique global ID of the away team's previous game (This gameid will be inaccurate/invalid in free trial as it is scrambled)

Name: HomeTeamPreviousGlobalGameID
Description: The unique global ID of the away team's previous game (This gameid will be inaccurate/invalid in free trial as it is scrambled)

Name: TournamentDisplayOrder
Description: The display order of this game. This is used for rendering NCAA Tournament bracket.

Name: TournamentDisplayOrderForHomeTeam
Description: The display order of the home team for this game. This is used for rendering the NCAA Tournament bracket; and it indicates whether the home team should be displayed at the top or bottom of the game card. Possible values: Top; Bottom

Name: Periods
Description: The details of the periods (halves & overtime) for this game.

Name: IsClosed
Description: Indicates whether the game is over and the final score has been verified and closed out.

Name: GameEndDateTime
Description: The date and time that the game ended in US Eastern Time

Name: Stadium
Description: The stadium details of where this game was played

Name: HomeRotationNumber
Description: Rotation number of home team for this game

Name: AwayRotationNumber
Description: Rotation number of away team for this game

Name: TournamentID
Description: The unique ID of the tournament

Name: Season
Description: The college basketball season of the tournament

Name: Name
Description: The name of the tournament

Name: Location
Description: The location of the tournament

Name: Games
Description: The games of this tournament

Name: LeftTopBracketConference
Description: The conference that is displayed on the top-left when rendering the tournament bracket.

Name: LeftBottomBracketConference
Description: The conference that is displayed on the bottom-left when rendering the tournament bracket.

Description: The conference that is displayed on the top-right when rendering the tournament bracket.

Name: RightBottomBracketConference
Description: The conference that is displayed on the bottom-right when rendering the tournament bracket.

Name: Game
Description: The game details of this box score

Name: Periods
Description: The period details of this box score

Name: PlayerGames
Description: The player game stats of this box score

Name: TeamGames
Description: The team game stats of this box score

Name: GameId
Description: The unique ID of the game.

Name: Season
Description: The calendar year of the season during which this game occurs.

Name: SeasonType
Description: The type of season that this record corresponds to (1=Regular Season; 2=Preseason; 3=Postseason; 4=Offseason; 5=AllStar).

Name: Day
Description: The day that the game is scheduled to be played in UTC.

Name: DateTime
Description: The date/time that the game is scheduled to be played in UTC.

Name: Status
Description: Indicates the game's status. Possible values include: Scheduled; InProgress; Final; Suspended; Postponed; Canceled

Name: AwayTeamId
Description: The TeamId of the away team.

Name: HomeTeamId
Description: The TeamId of the home team.

Name: AwayTeamName
Description: The name of the away team.

Name: HomeTeamName
Description: The name of the home team.

Name: GlobalGameId
Description: A globally unique ID for this game. This value is guaranteed to be unique across all sports/leagues.

Name: GlobalAwayTeamId
Description: A globally unique ID for the away team. This value is guaranteed to be unique across all sports/leagues.

Name: GlobalHomeTeamId
Description: A globally unique ID for the home team. This value is guaranteed to be unique across all sports/leagues.

Name: PregameOdds
Description: List of Pregame GameOdds from different sportsbooks

Name: LiveOdds
Description: List of Live GameOdds from different sportsbooks

Name: HomeTeamScore
Description: Score of the home team (updated after game ends to allow for resolving bets)

Name: AwayTeamScore
Description: Score of the away team (updated after game ends to allow for resolving bets)

Name: TotalScore
Description: Total scored points in the game (updated after game ends to allow for resolving bets)

Name: HomeRotationNumber
Description: Rotation number of home team for this game

Name: AwayRotationNumber
Description: Rotation number of away team for this game

Name: AlternateMarketPregameOdds
Description: List of Alternate Market Pregame GameOdds from different sportsbooks

Name: GameOddId
Description: Unique ID of this odd

Name: Sportsbook
Description: Name of sportsbook

Name: GameId
Description: The unique ID of the game

Name: Created
Description: The timestamp of when these odds were first created; based on US Eatern Time (EST/EDT).

Name: Updated
Description: The timestamp of when these odds were last updated; based on US Eatern Time (EST/EDT). If these are the latest odds for this game; and they have not been updated within the last few minutes; then it indicates that there were problems connecting to the sportsbook.

Name: HomeMoneyLine
Description: The sportsbook's money line for the home team

Name: AwayMoneyLine
Description: The sportsbook's money line for the away team

Name: HomePointSpread
Description: The sportsbook's point spread for the home team

Name: AwayPointSpread
Description: The sportsbook's point spread for the away team

Name: HomePointSpreadPayout
Description: The sportsbook's point spread payout for the home team

Name: AwayPointSpreadPayout
Description: The sportsbook's point spread payout for the away team

Name: OverUnder
Description: The sportsbook's total points scored over under for the game

Name: OverPayout
Description: The sportsbook's payout for the over

Name: UnderPayout
Description: The sportsbook's payout for the under

Name: SportsbookId
Description: Unique ID of the sportsbook

Name: OddType
Description: The odd type of this specific odd
